Class ApplicationManager

java.lang.Object
main.control.dataManagers.DataManager
main.control.dataManagers.ApplicationManager
public class ApplicationManager extends DataManager
Manages BTO applications in the system. Includes functionality for applying for flats, viewing applications, and handling withdrawals.
